Posts.Content: Around my period each month, I get this tender spot feeling on my right breast, like it is right on top of the bone, right inbetween the breasts but on the right breast. Also, that breast is always slightly bigger than the other. I'm not even 20 years old. How do you know what is a lump, and what is your bone/muscle/flesh/ducts/normal parts?
Posts.Title: Breast Lumps
